## 3. Quiz Section

Interactive quiz with progress bar, question, and answer grid.

### PHP

```php
<section class="quiz-section" id="quiz">
    <div class="question-container">
        <div class="progress-bar"></div>
        <div class="quiz-content">
            <h2 id="question" class="quiz-question-text"></h2>
            <div id="options" class="options-container"></div>
            <button id="quiz-cta" class="cta-button" style="display: none;">Continue</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="results-container" style="display: none;"></div>
</section>
```

### SCSS Skeleton

```scss
.quiz-section {
    background-color: colors.$color-gray-medium;
    padding: 48px 64px 64px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;

    @media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
        padding: 32px;
    }

    @media #{layout.$small-screen-and-smaller} {
        padding: 24px 15px;
    }

    .progress-bar {
        display: flex;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 632px;

        .progress-segment {
            flex: 1;
            height: 4px;
            background-color: colors.$color-white;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;

            &.active {
                background-color: colors.$color-green-dark;
            }
        }
    }

    .quiz-content {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 24px;
        width: 632px;
        max-width: 100%;
    }

    #question {
        font-family: fonts.$STIX-Two-Text;
        font-weight: 400;
        font-size: 40px;
        line-height: 48px;
        text-align: center;
        color: colors.$color-black;

        @media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
            font-size: 36px;
            line-height: 40px;
        }

        @media #{layout.$small-screen-and-smaller} {
            font-size: 28px;
            line-height: 32px;
        }
    }

    .options-container {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 312px);
        gap: 18px;
        justify-content: center;

        @media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        }

        @media #{layout.$small-screen-and-smaller} {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }

    .option-button {
        height: 64px;
        padding: 12px 32px;
        border-radius: 2px;
        border: none;
        background-color: colors.$color-white;
        color: colors.$color-black;
        font-family: fonts.$DM-Sans;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 24px;
        letter-spacing: 0.8px;
        cursor: pointer;
        box-shadow: 0px 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0px 10px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.09);

        &.selected,
        &:hover {
            background-color: colors.$color-black;
            color: colors.$color-white;
        }

        @media #{layout.$small-screen-and-smaller} {
            height: auto;
            padding: 16px;
        }
    }

    .results-container {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 632px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
}
```

